text: Christine Palau (11 June 1930 - 26 November 2014) was a French gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2014 deaths Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Paris
